OL,3,CLearning disabilities service could
OL,4,Cbecome blueprint to save NHS billions
OL,6,FDr Dipti Patil is a Consultant
OL,7,FPsychiatrist for Pennine Care NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust and one of the team
OL,9,Fthat established Radcliffe Place.
OL,11,FDr Patil said: "What we do here is
OL,12,Fgive the system a break when people
OL,13,Fare in crisis... when somebody comes
OL,14,Fin we assess their needs in the
OL,15,Fcommunity, and then we develop an
OL,16,Funderstanding of what led to the
OL,17,Fcrisis and what can be done in the
OL,18,Ffuture to not let that crisis happen
OL,19,Fagain."
