OL,3,CLearning disabilities service could
OL,4,Cbecome blueprint to save NHS billions
OL,6,FClinicians say people with learning
OL,7,Fdisabilities are often misdiagnosed
OL,8,Fwith mental health conditions and then
OL,9,Fwrongly medicated.
OL,11,FDr Patil said: "It's an incredibly
OL,12,Fdangerous thing to do because people
OL,13,Fwith learning disabilities already
OL,14,Fhave physical health problems.
OL,16,F"On top of that if you give them
OL,17,Fmedication that they don't require it
OL,18,Fcould lead to their liver failure,
OL,19,Fkidney failure and ultimately lead to
OL,20,Ftheir death."
