OL,3,CLearning disabilities service could
OL,4,Cbecome blueprint to save NHS billions
OL,6,FMr Moroney visits his son every day at
OL,7,FRadcliffe Place and had seen a massive
OL,8,Fchange in his behaviour and moods.
OL,10,FHe said: "It is a very calm
OL,11,Fenvironment and it's been purposefully
OL,12,Fdesigned to help people of Sonny's
OL,13,Fdisposition. The staff are lovely.
OL,14,FSonny is happy here."
OL,16,FThe unit opened a year ago and
OL,17,Fcurrently has four beds. Patients are
OL,18,Fmonitored 24 hours a day so the team
OL,19,Fcan get a better understanding of
OL,20,Ftheir needs, and experts say this type
OL,21,Fof support has never been needed more.
OL,26,@rD@JOUvD@UO]
