OL,6,FAccording to ITV News FOI data,
OL,7,Fanalysed by Mencap:
OL,9,FDan Scorer, Head of Policy & Public
OL,10,FAffairs at Mencap, said Radcliffe
OL,11,FPlace is a good example of the kind of
OL,12,Fsupport needed in every area of the
OL,13,Fcountry.
