OL,3,CLearning disabilities service could
OL,4,Cbecome blueprint to save NHS billions
OL,6,FMr Scorer said: "We need more places
OL,7,Fwhere if someone is in crisis in the
OL,8,Fcommunity they can go for a short
OL,9,Fperiod of time and get the support
OL,10,Fthey need and where arrangements can
OL,11,Fbe put in place for them then to be
OL,12,Fable to make a return back to their
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,F"We also need to see more Early
OL,16,FIntervention Services where we are
OL,17,Fsupporting people before they reach
OL,18,Fcrisis. Crisis is not a state anyone
OL,19,Fshould be left to get to."
