OL,3,CLearning disabilities service could
OL,4,Cbecome blueprint to save NHS billions
OL,6,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "The NHS has
OL,7,Fincreased investment in community
OL,8,Fsupport to enable more people with a
OL,9,Flearning disability and autistic
OL,10,Fpeople to receive personalised care in
OL,11,Fthe community, and while there is more
OL,12,Fto do, progress has been made, with
OL,13,Fthe number of people with these
OL,14,Fconditions in a mental health hospital
OL,15,Fbeing reduced by 30% since 2015, and
OL,16,Fthe number with a learning disability
OL,17,Fbeing reduced by 60%.
OL,26,@nD@[OU
