OL,3,CLearning disabilities service could
OL,4,Cbecome blueprint to save NHS billions
OL,6,F"Staff continue to work hard to ensure
OL,7,Fpatients are discharged into community
OL,8,Fsettings safely and in a timely way,
OL,9,Fand the NHS will be working with local
OL,10,Fsystems this year to ensure all areas
OL,11,Fhave plans in place to address the
OL,12,Fincrease in the number of autistic
OL,13,Fpeople and continue to ensure people
OL,14,Fare admitted only where necessary for
OL,15,Fmental health treatment."
